---
// A component to display related resources at the bottom of blog posts
---

<div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Boost Your Productivity</h3>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <a href="/tools/gpa-calculator" class="group block p-6 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-100 transition-colors border border-blue-100">
      <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0a2351] group-hover:text-blue-700 mb-2">GPA Calculator &rarr;</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Calculate your current GPA and see exactly what grades you need to hit your target.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/printables/weekly-planner" class="group block p-6 bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-100 transition-colors border border-indigo-100">
      <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-indigo-900 group-hover:text-indigo-700 mb-2">Weekly Planner Printable &rarr;</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Download our free printable weekly planner to organize your classes and study blocks.</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
